import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { ContextProvider } from './Context/context'

//const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))

ReactDOM.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
     <ContextProvider>
      <App />
      </ContextProvider>
    </React.StrictMode>,
    document.getElementById('root')
  );
